map <C-v> "+gP
imap <C-v> <S-Insert>
map <C-c> "+y
imap <C-c> "+y
map <F9> o<Esc>p<Esc>
map <S-TAB> << V
vmap <S-TAB> << V
map <TAB> >> 
vmap <TAB> >>
" 插入模式命令
imap <C-h> <BS>
imap <C-g> <Left>
imap <C-l> <Right>
imap <C-k> <Up>
imap <C-j> <Down>
" end
" 注释star
nnoremap <C-Up> I/*<cr>
imap <C-Up> <Home>/*<cr>
nnoremap <C-Down> A*/
imap <C-Down> <End> */
" shift+Left注释反注释
nmap <C-Left> I//<ESC>
imap <C-Left> <Home>//<ESC>
nmap <C-Right> <Home>xx<ESC>
imap <C-Right> <Home><Right><Right><BS><BS><ESC>
" 注释 end

" 设置leader键
let mapleader="'"
nnoremap <Leader>q  :w<CR>
" (上下翻页)
nnoremap <Leader>d  <C-d>
nnoremap <Leader>u  <C-u>

" markdown code block
map <C--> i```<Enter><Esc>O
imap <C--> <Esc><C-->
imap <C-y> ###<Space>
map <C-y> i###<Space>

imap <C-]> ####<Space>
map <C-]> i####<Space>

" idea内置

"显示当前文件路径
nnoremap <Leader>s :action ShowFilePath<CR>

nnoremap <Leader>e :action SelectIn<CR>

nnoremap <Leader>a :action RecentFiles<CR>

" GotoFile 相当于ctrl+p
nnoremap <C-p> :action GotoFile<CR>

nnoremap <Leader>q :action OpenInBrowser<CR>

nnoremap <Leader>t :action Terminal.OpenInTerminal<CR>

" 隐藏侧边项目栏 
"nnoremap <Leader>a :action ActivateProjectToolWindow<CR>
nnoremap <Leader>h :action ActivateProjectToolWindow<CR>

nnoremap <Leader>y :action ToggleFindInSelection<CR>

"相当于IDEA的两次shift按钮
"nnoremap <Leader>se :action SearchEverywhere<CR>
"
nnoremap <Leader>fs :action ToggleFullScreen<CR>

nnoremap <C-A-l> :action ReformatCode<CR>

"跳转到Action
nnoremap <Leader>ga :action GotoAction<CR>

" 重命名文件
nnoremap <Leader>rf :action RenameFile<CR>
